Independent schools strive to prepare their students for further and higher education, their chosen career and their place as world citizens.
As an educational sector that can design and implement a custom-made school curriculum, we see that modern languages remain popular and desirable subjects outstanding within schools.
Nelson Mandela said, "If you talk to someone in a language he understands, you reach his head.
